\cf0 \
The length of the sequence is set in the \'93Steps\'94 box (1 - 64), but remember, this is only the maximum length, because the point at which the sequence starts and loops back can be defined with the black Loop bar on the top of the interface.\
\
The \'93Fold\'94 toggle lets you have the notes that are active in the sequence be the only ones displayed on the interface.\
\
The main interface lets you edit 5 different parameters and can show all of them at the same time, this is chosen in the \'93Edit\'94 menu in the bottom right corner:\
\
Show all - Shows pitch and all the parameters in the background and edits pitch\
\
Pitch - Shows and edits pitch\
\
Velocity - Shows and edits velocity\
\
Duration - Shows and edits duration\
\
Mod 1/2 - Shows and edits Mod1/2\
\
