\cf0 Presets\
\pard\tx566\tx1133\tx1700\tx2267\tx2834\tx3401\tx3968\tx4535\tx5102\tx5669\tx6236\tx6803\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
In the bottom left corner there is a section to save and real presets within the module, the \'93Preset\'94 box (1 - 16).\
\
There is also an option of cycling through the presets automatically within a range (starting from 1) defined in the box next to the toggle button \'93Cycle\'94.\
The cycling occurs after the last step of the loop, entering a new preset when it loops back.\
\
There are four options available for the type of cycling:\
\
Up - increments the preset number by 1 and loops back to the first one.\
\
Down - decrements the preset number and loops forward to the last one.\
\
U&D - increments the preset number until the last one, then starts decrementing until the first one and so on\'85\
\
Random - a preset is randomly chosen from those that have not been chosen once (it goes through all of them until one of them is repeated).\
\
